@startuml UC-05_View_Profile

title UC-05: View User Profile

skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #E0F2F1
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #004D40
skinparam ActivityFontColor #1B5E20
skinparam ArrowColor #004D40

start
:User navigates to Profile page;
:System displays loading skeleton;
:FirebaseService.get_user_profile(uid) called;
:Firestore retrieves user document from users/{uid};
:System populates profile UI sections:\n- Basic Info (avatar, name, email, member since)\n- Profile Details (first/last name, bio, company, job title, location, social links)\n- Usage Statistics (workflows, API calls, storage, team members, integrations)\n- Subscription Info (plan, billing cycle, next billing date, status)\n- Activity (last login, last active feature, session count, time spent)\n- Preferences (theme, language, timezone, notifications)\n- Connected Integrations (list of connected services, disconnect options);

:User can edit profile fields;
:System validates changes;
if (Validation passed?) then (Yes)
    :FirebaseService.update_user_profile() called;
    :Firestore updates user document;
    :System shows success notification;
    :UI refreshes with updated data;
else (No)
    :Display error messages;
endif

:Analytics logs "profile_viewed" event;
:Profile page displayed;
stop

@enduml
